  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>From our humble beginnings as a used car trader in the 1970s, Prime Group has evolved to become a multi-award winning diversified company that has continuously reinvented ourselves over the past 50 years. Today, we are a leader in motor and commercial vehicle trade, car rental, taxi and private-hire services as well as fuels marketing. We are also proud to be one of the Top Entrepreneurial Businesses in Singapore - for our ideas, strategies and leading the industry to provide the best for our clients.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join Prime Taxi to become a full-time taxi driver where you can manage your own income and time. Send us your resume with contact details and receive guidance from our experienced consultants.</p><p></p>",
